    "Title": "Shutdown CFP\u2019s Comms",
    "Description": "CFP think they\u2019re safe over at <EM4>~mission(Location|Address)</EM4> but we got big plans for them. You\u2019re gonna pave the way for us by heading there and shutting down their comm towers.\n\nThere should be a <EM4>control terminal at the top</EM4> that you can use to shut the tower down. You get that sorted and they won\u2019t be able to call for backup. Then we can show those skags who this system belongs to.\n\nMost outposts use the same system, so this\u2019ll come in handy next time you want to make sure reinforcements don\u2019t mess with you.\n\n\nStows out.",
